{"tid":2373263,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"想入行證券dealer/cs/settlement會唔會做唔黎","createTime":"2021-01-20T10:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T11:49:40.000Z","uid":216586,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dec2a195bdcdbd7abe08b997ed073c2aab0726af","tid":2373263,"uid":216586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:10:56.000Z","msg":"終極乞食科廢top up grad做左幾個月垃圾文職工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全感受到文職工幾垃圾同埋完全無career path可言<br />\n見證券行只要考幾個試就可以apply，雖然個個都話夕陽行業，但我估點都好過垃圾文職工完全學唔到野掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身我自己0 finance底，股票期權都係最近開始溫證券考試資料先認識多左，所以我有d驚第時入到去做會唔會做唔黎（本身轉數唔算快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），驚落錯盤或者識唔哂d股票產品比人小到pk。<br />\n有無做開證券產品既ching講下呢幾個post會做d咩同埋易唔易出錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d14259dfba8eda379a1861f185902d592fc8d3d","tid":2373263,"uid":45035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:13:58.000Z","msg":"入銀行做好公式化 <br />\n入證券行睇你遇唔遇到好人 學到好多野"},{"pid":"761503c9b8b2c959bbeead6d69f01a72e900ab1a","tid":2373263,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"做過幾個月Settlement，吃力唔討好又忙，好多野都將會 automation , 大公司唔單止要搞 BAU仲要整project野"},{"pid":"91cb76dfef239730ea25b49b4fa0afda9f152cbe","tid":2373263,"uid":57338,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"唔會 因為有手有腳都做到"},{"pid":"1da1b5fe53b469fd6b9c63ca12c9e9be8a336c6a","tid":2373263,"uid":216586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761503c9b8b2c959bbeead6d69f01a72e900ab1a","tid":2373263,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"做過幾個月Settlement，吃力唔討好又忙，好多野都將會 automation , 大公司唔單止要搞 BAU仲要整project野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"巴打而家做緊咩位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj